                                                                                <td class="mcnTextContent" style="padding: 0px 18px 9px; line-height: 150%;" valign="top">

                                                                                    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-409b4f41-7fff-6466-ea68-380cc5982c83" style="font-weight:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Hello Seller!</span></strong><br></p>
                                                                                    <br>
                                                                                    <strong id="docs-internal-guid-409b4f41-7fff-6466-ea68-380cc5982c83" style="font-weight:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">We have received your details and are reviewing it to make sure we can help you to grow on the Facebook marketplace.
</span></strong>
                                                                                    </p>
                                                                                    <strong id="docs-internal-guid-409b4f41-7fff-6466-ea68-380cc5982c83" style="font-weight:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">
We will get back to you soon with the update and further process.
&nbsp;
Meanwhile you can check the basic requirement for Facebook marketplace (we still have some more parameters to estimate the seller growth on the platform) &nbsp;<br><br>PreRequisites  to sell on Facebook Marketplace:
</span></strong>

                                                                                    <ul dir="ltr">
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6318400f-7fff-f14d-fd9a-4ed8fc3b3693" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><strong id="docs-internal-guid-c6de8925-7fff-4055-3b21-07dae8d2b2e4" style="font-weight:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Have a Federal Tax Identification Number that matches merchant’s legal name
</span></strong></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">A State Tax Registration Number for every state where merchant does business</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Have a US-based bank account to set up payouts
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Have a physical business address and email address
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Have a business representative name, SSN and DOB
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Have a customer service email
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Must comply with our Merchant Policies, including:
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Fulfill (ship) orders within 3 business days of purchase
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Offer a 30-day or longer return policy
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Respond to all customer inquiries within 2 business days (via the customer service email address specified in commerce settings)
</span></li>
                                                                                        <li style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-1df939f8-7fff-7863-009a-dda876faabe4" style="font-weight:normal"></strong><strong style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap"></strong><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Must comply with Facebook’s Commerce Policies
</span></li>
                                                                                    </ul>

                                                                                    <strong id="docs-internal-guid-409b4f41-7fff-6466-ea68-380cc5982c83" style="font-weight:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Let me know a suitable time to fix a call for a better understanding or feel free to write back.</span></strong><br>
                                                                                    <br>
                                                                                    <strong id="docs-internal-guid-409b4f41-7fff-6466-ea68-380cc5982c83" style="font-weight:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:12.499999999999998pt; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:400; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:pre-wrap">Thanks,<br> Team Cedcommerce
&nbsp;</span></strong>
                                                                                </td>
                                                                            </tr>
